## 2. CUSTOMER ORDERS

### Create Order (Customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Platform: mobile

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "quantity": 2,
  "destination": "Jalan Merdeka No. 123, Jakarta"
}

### Get My Order History (Customer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/my-history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Platform: mobile

### Get Order Offers
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/offers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Platform: mobile

